{"tid":1419942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家已經發展成街坊挑戰狗狗，正苦呢次頭痕了","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:06:54.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d29e45bceb0482c14fa600dad45c7dfc10c2fb4","tid":1419942,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"2014年果招，2019年已經唔work, 狗狗放題式出tg係比不合作運動更擾民，我都唔講狗狗用過期tg更加毒。<br />\n<br />\nCap少少新聞，我唔cap黃大仙同西環，呢兩單全港皆知<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/434155540508935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F434155540508935&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=4da6725c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/434155540508935</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【8.5<strong> 沙田</strong>】居民警察深夜互罵ㅤ「閂燈瞓覺啦！」<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上於沙田鄉事會路及源禾路交界清場，有沙田居民不滿警方強光照向民居，在單位內罵向防線的警員，指「唔好再射得唔得，睇唔清楚？無街燈咩？」有女警反罵居民「你瞓覺啦，閂燈瞓覺啦！」、「又話瞓覺又唔閂燈！又話人地射住你！」，該居民再反駁「你理得我！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190806/s00001/1565021079711/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565021079711%2F&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=5f55b1fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565021079711%2F&h=c8d7e3c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190806/s00001/1565021079711/</a><br />\n<br />\n【00:35】<strong>屯門</strong>警方發放催淚彈期間，示威者掟石還擊，之後已大致散去。V city瓏門居民指罵防暴警察為「黑警」，批評警方在民居附近發放多枚催淚彈，令氣味攻入民居。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190806/s00001/1565030053047/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565030053047%2F&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=c2fe5d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565030053047%2F&h=66a8823f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190806/s00001/1565030053047/</a><br />\n<br />\n多間警署被圍，警方大量放催淚彈，惹來附近居民投訴，示威者傍晚約6時一度包圍<strong>荃灣</strong>新界南警察總部，防暴警察衝出總部外施放催淚彈，有荃灣花園居民在平台大呼「無辜」，換來警員以粗言喝罵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/8-5-%E6%80%92%E7%81%AB%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%97%E8%BE%B1%E5%BE%8C-%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%81%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%94%BB%E9%98%B2%E6%88%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-5-%25E6%2580%2592%25E7%2581%25AB%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D-%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2594%25BB%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2588%25B0%2F&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=f5985b24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-5-%25E6%2580%2592%25E7%2581%25AB%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D-%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2594%25BB%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2588%25B0%2F&h=b0d4ed8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/8-5-%E6%80%92%E7%81%AB%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%97%E8%BE%B1%E5%BE%8C-%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%81%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%94%BB%E9%98%B2%E6%88%B0/</a><br />\n<br />\n晚上 8 至 9 時之間，一旦有零星市民欲走出天耀路、或從天盛苑行人路走出來，警方便會密集式發放一輪催淚彈，示威者仿傚黃大仙街坊準備了蒸餸用的銻碟掩蓋催淚彈，但仍有無口罩街坊誤吸毒煙不適。有被捕支援律師因無法打通<strong>天水圍</strong>警署電話，故直接到場尋找被捕者，在閘外等候期間，背後的催淚彈亦如煙花爆發。天盛苑天橋上圍觀的街坊則不時怒罵警察「黑社會！黑社會！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190806/s00001/1565021225726/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565021225726%2F&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=937352de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565021225726%2F&h=ae479e63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190806/s00001/1565021225726/</a><br />\n<br />\n【8月5日23:32】晚上10時多，<strong>大埔</strong>太和路已不見示威者。另一邊廂，近新興花園、大埔警署外，有防暴警察持長盾戒備，不少街坊大叫「黑警可恥」、「大埔唔歡迎你哋」。其間逾10名警員上前轉上天橋，市民四散後再集合，大叫「香港警察知法犯法」等口號。有人用雷射燈照向警方，警方用強光照向市民。至晚上11時多，部分在天橋上的警員，走到樓梯戒備，市民仍未散去。"}]}